data.description: This beautifully maintained ground floor end unit in desirable Wynwood Estates has so much to offer - new hardwood floors, recently remodeled master and guest bathrooms both with Bluetooth speaker mirrors! Master bedroom has a large wardrobe closet and a second closet. The spacious living room has sliders that leads to a large patio. Close to shopping center and public transportation.  One year home warranty included!  Showing begins on 2/9/24
